public class PersonAdminData
extends AbstractUserData<PersonAdminData>

The class is used to define all administration person (which have no related person business object) objects used to create / update and to export.

append4CIFileValues

protected void append4CIFileValues(StringBuilder _cmd)
Appends the person specific values to the TCL update code _cmd of the configuration item file. This includes:
  • access
  • administration access
  • types
  • groups
  • roles
  • password never expires flag
  • wants email flag
  • wants icon mail flag

checkExport

public void checkExport(ExportParser _exportParser)
                 throws matrix.util.MatrixException
Checks the export of this person if all values are correct defined. It is checked that
  • all access is correct defined
  • all administration access is correct defined
  • all groups are correct defined
  • all roles are correct defined
  • password never expires flag is defined if set to true
  • wants email flag is correct defined
  • wants icon mail flag is correct defined

Overrides:
checkExport in class AbstractUserData<PersonAdminData>
Parameters:
_exportParser - parsed export
Throws:
matrix.util.MatrixException - if check failed
